# Pose & Poise Brand Style Guide — STRICT ENFORCEMENT

When writing CSS, styling components, or creating UI for this project, you MUST follow these standards exactly. Do not deviate.

## Typography — REQUIRED

**Fonts (no substitutes allowed):**
- Display/Headlines: `'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif` (weights: 300, 400, 500, 600)
- Body/UI: `'Outfit', sans-serif` (weights: 300, 400, 500)

**FORBIDDEN fonts:** Inter, Roboto, Arial, system-ui, sans-serif (as primary)

**Type Scale:**
| Element | Size | Weight | Font |
|---------|------|--------|------|
| Hero H1 | `clamp(48px, 8vw, 96px)` | 300 | Cormorant Garamond |
| Section H2 | `clamp(36px, 6vw, 64px)` | 300 | Cormorant Garamond |
| Card H3 | `24px` | 400 | Cormorant Garamond |
| Body | `15px-16px` | 300 | Outfit |
| Label/Overline | `12px` | 400, uppercase, `letter-spacing: 4px` | Outfit |

## Colors — EXACT VALUES REQUIRED

```css
--color-cream: #FAF9F7;      /* Primary background */
--color-charcoal: #1A1A1A;   /* Text, buttons, dark sections */
--color-camel: #C4A484;      /* Accent, CTAs, highlights */
--color-white: #FFFFFF;      /* Cards, feature backgrounds */
```

**Text opacity levels:**
- Secondary: `rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.7)`
- Tertiary: `rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.6)`
- Muted: `rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.4)`

**FORBIDDEN:** Purple gradients, blue accents, generic grays (#666, #999, etc.)

## Border Radius — STRICT

Use `border-radius: 0` throughout for sharp, editorial aesthetic.
**Only exceptions:** Decorative circles (`50%`), code blocks (`4px`)

**FORBIDDEN:** Rounded corners on buttons, cards, inputs, or containers

## Buttons — EXACT SPEC

```css
.button {
  background: #1A1A1A;
  color: #FAF9F7;
  padding: 18px 48px;
  font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 0;
  transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}
.button:hover {
  background: #C4A484;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(196, 164, 132, 0.3);
}
```

## Transitions & Animations

- Primary easing: `cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)` with `0.4s` duration
- Simple easing: `0.3s ease`
- Entrance animation: `fadeUp` (translateY 30px → 0, opacity 0 → 1)

## Cards & Glass Effects

```css
.card {
  padding: 40px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.05);
  border-radius: 0;
}
.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  border-color: rgba(196, 164, 132, 0.3);
}
```

